sequenceDiagram
    participant Crawler
    participant Note as Note A
    participant Sidecar as link-index/A.json
    participant Rewriter
    participant Map as URL to filename map
    Crawler->>Note: Write [text](S2V_LINK_0)
    Crawler->>Sidecar: Store S2V_LINK_0 to URL B
    Note over Crawler: ... all pages crawled ...
    Rewriter->>Sidecar: Read S2V_LINK_0
    Rewriter->>Map: Look up URL B
    alt URL B is in vault
        Rewriter->>Note: Replace with [[B|text]]
    else External URL
        Rewriter->>Note: Replace with [text](URL B)
    end
